程序包 vincent.utils

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CarTimer
    timer for calculating how many hours are car having park
    DatFileFilter
    this is filter class for JFileChooser to filter file not matching extension of JFileChooser
    ReadUtil
    read util for reading data
    SingletonFactory
    the factory class to create EnterTable object, the purpose is only one EnterTable object can be create at the same time
    SqlHelper
    sql helper class for create connection object and close the resource
